Package Model.Messages

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DotsMessage
    Empty interface that extends serializable to serialise implementing objects All messages sent over sockets will extend this interface, so that when we read the message, we simply have to do e.g if (message instanceOf DotsMessageResponse) { }, to deal with the message accordingly Created by JiaHao on 24/3/15.
